The paper discusses the problem of combining existing skills to solve new tasks in reinforcement learning, which is a core problem in machine learning. The paper proposes a method for optimal value function composition, which is a technique used in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
